name: Endurance into Max Aerobic
description:
After a good warm up, we are going to build some endurance and fatigue, before preparing yourself for a Max Aerobic interval. We can't always start the intervals with fresh legs. By including Zone 2 endurance before the high intensity work, the session provides a different training stimulus.
